      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/zh/write-professionally.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/write-professionally/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/write-professionally/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/write-professionally/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;write-professionally&#34;&gt;Write professionally&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Read over your compositions, and wherever you meet with a passage which you think is particularly fine, strike it out.&lt;/em&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samuel_Johnson&#34;&gt;Samuel Johnson&lt;/a&gt;, quoted in “ &lt;a href=&#34;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Life_of_Samuel_Johnson&#34;&gt;The Life of Samuel Johnson&lt;/a&gt; “, by &lt;a href=&#34;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Boswell&#34;&gt;James Boswell&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This advice is mainly for first-time authors.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A journal article is going to be a permanent record of your work; thus it is important that these articles are as professionally written as possible, so as not to cause embarrassment several years from now.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
